----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This program is a simple vocabulary trainer based on text files.
For the syntax of the vocalbluray db, see the example file (vok_ex.txt).

There is no installation required, simply run it via ` $./SVocTrainer.pl ' (you have to make it exutable with ' $chmod a+x SVocTrainer.pl ` initially).

Requirements:
- an actual perl distribution
- the additional perl module "Switch".

